<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIXON'S FUNERAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Former President Richard Nixon's funeral today in Yorba Linda will be carried 
live on radio and television. 
</P>
<P>
 Coverage of the funeral, which is scheduled to begin at 4 p.m. at the Nixon 
Library, will be seen on CBS, NBC, ABC, KTLA Channel 5, KCAL Channel 9, KTTV 
Channel 11, KCET Channel 28, KVEA Channel 52, CNN and C-SPAN. 
</P>
<P>
 On radio, KNX (1070) will broadcast the funeral from 4-5 p.m. and KFWB (980) 
will offer reports throughout the day. 
</P>
