TERRORISM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rwanda, Bosnia, Somalia, Israel, South Africa, North Korea. So, the Cold War 
is over; now we have scattered showers of terror.  
</P>
<P>
 ENO CLEVERINGA 
</P>
