NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Ken Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Alonzo King artistic director of LINES Contemporary Ballet in San Francisco, 
has been named a UC Regents' Lecturer at UC Irvine. He will be in residence at 
the UCI dance department May 23-27 and will give a free lecture demonstration 
on May 26 in the Fine Arts Village Theatre. LINES appeared last month at the 
Irvine Barclay Theatre as part of the "Feet First Contemporary Dance Series." 
(714) 856-6929. 
</P>
