 Jeff Capel, who coached North Carolina A&T into the NCAA tournament in his 
first season, was hired to coach at Old Dominion. Hockey 
</P>
<P>
 A Russian has pleaded guilty in Buffalo, N.Y., to a charge of menacing Alex 
Mogilny of the Buffalo Sabres, whom he was accused of threatening in an 
extortion attempt. 
</P>
<P>
 Serguei Fomitchev, 31, agreed to the plea on a lesser charge to avoid a long 
wait in jail for an extortion trial and a possible prison term of up to seven 
years, his lawyer said. 
</P>
<P>
