<P>
RAIN WASHES OUT HIGH SCHOOL AND COMMUNITY COLLEGE EVENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 All three Orange Empire Conference community college baseball games involving 
county teams that were scheduled Tuesday were postponed because of wet grounds. 
</P>
<P>
 Golden West at Orange Coast, Riverside at Cypress and Fullerton at Saddleback 
were rescheduled at 2:30 today. 
</P>
<P>
 The Orange Empire softball game between Irvine Valley and Fullerton was 
canceled. 
</P>
<P>
 High school postponements included: 
</P>
<P>
 Prep baseball -- Century League: Canyon at El Modena postponed to today; 
Foothill at Santa Ana Valley postponed to Thursday; Orange at Villa Park 
postponed to a later date. Garden Grove League: Pacifica at Kennedy postponed 
to Thursday. Olympic League: Whittier Christian at Orange Lutheran and Ontario 
Christian at Calvary Chapel postponed to today. Pacific Coast League: Laguna 
Beach at Century and Trabuco Hills at Estancia postponed to today; Costa Mesa 
at Laguna Hills postponed to Thursday. Sunset League: Fountain Valley at 
Servite postponed to today; Huntington Beach at Santa Ana postponed to a later 
date; Friday's Servite at Huntington Beach game has been moved to Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
 Prep softball -- Arrowhead League: La Sierra Academy vs. Southern California 
Christian at Hart Park will be rescheduled at a later date. Century League: 
Canyon at Villa Park and Santa Ana Valley at Orange rescheduled to Monday. 
Empire League: Loara at Esperanza rescheduled to today; El Dorado vs. Cypress 
at Oak Knoll Park rescheduled to May 4; Los Alamitos at Katella rescheduled to 
a later date. Express League: Rolling Hills Prep at Heritage Christian 
rescheduled at a later date. Freeway League: Troy at Sunny Hills postponed to 
Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 Garden Grove League: Rancho Alamitos vs. Garden Grove at Twain School and 
Kennedy at Los Amigos postponed to today. Olympic League: Brethren Christian at 
Orange Lutheran postponed to today; Calvary Chapel vs. Capistrano Valley 
Christian at San Clemente Sports Complex postponed to a later date. Orange 
League: Western at Savanna and Magnolia vs. Valencia at Kramer Jr. High 
postponed to Friday; Brea-Olinda at Anaheim postponed to a later date. Pacific 
Coast League: Trabuco Hills at Costa Mesa postponed to Friday; Laguna Hills at 
Century postponed to Monday. Sunset League: Fountain Valley vs. Rosary at Lions 
Field postponed to May 5; Marina at Westminster postponed to a later date. 
</P>
<P>
 Prep tennis -- Century League: Villa Park at Foothill tentatively postponed to 
Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Prep track -- Olympic League: Brethren Christian vs. Capistrano Valley 
Christian at Los Alamitos High postponed to a later date. 
</P>
