<HEADLINE>
<P>
ROCKET LAUNCH CALLED OFF 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Air Force called off Tuesday's planned launch of a Titan rocket with a 
secret spy satellite because of a technical problem in the final seconds. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
