<HEADLINE>
<P>
EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Capital Cities-ABC Inc. said its earnings doubled in the first quarter due to 
rising advertising demand and stronger performances in its broadcasting, cable 
TV and newspaper businesses. 
</P>
<P>
