<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042794-0244 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 036335 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 27, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 12; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
