<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY: NONA MORELLI'S WILL ACQUIRE DENVER FIRM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Italian foods maker Nona Morelli's II Inc. said Tuesday that it has signed a 
deal to acquire Fantastic Foods International Inc. in a stock swap valued at 
$1.6 million.Under the deal, Denver-based Fantastic Foods will become a 
subsidiary of Nona Morelli's II in Irvine. In turn, Nona Morelli's II will sell 
the assets of its domestic food manufacturing and distribution business to 
Fantastic Foods. 
</P>
<P>
 Nona Morelli's said Fantastic Foods intends to apply for listing on the Nasdaq 
market within 90 days. 
</P>
<P>
 Nona Morelli's II makes fresh pasta and other Italian food. Fantastic Food 
makes meals in a cup, soups and other foods. 
</P>
</TEXT>
