<P>
 Section Editor: Ray F. Herndon Design Editor: Chuck Nigash News Editor: Laura 
Nott Photo Editor: Don Tormey Photographers: Bob Grieser and Robert Lachman, 
and photographs from The Times library and wire services Staff Writers: Alicia 
